{"type":"message","id":"defcc305","parentId":"524f46e5","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:22:37.283Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wmd8x33m6gic_2","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"07cdf349780f84851f44e5ab68761cdbe5f6e4a62559b8fbf3f07e739935bf41\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 46,\n      \"score\": 0.7409701336581583,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7409701336581583,\n      \"snippet\": \"# AHV DTLX Project Context\\n\\n_Last updated: 2026-04-12 by Orbis_\\n\\n## ⚠️ CRITICAL — System Architecture\\n\\n**DTLX và QLHV là 2 hệ thống DÙNG CHUNG database:**\\n\\n```\\nDTLX (MASTER) ─────────────────── QLHV (SUBSYSTEM)\\n   Hệ thống chính                    Tách ra cho THẦY/GV\\n   Ban giám đốc, Sales, Admin        Giáo viên quản lý HV\\n        │                                 │\\n        └──────── SHARED MONGODB ────────┘\\n              103.253.21.98:27017\\n```\\n\\n**→ QLHV phải đồng bộ dữ liệu với DTLX luôn luôn.**\\n**→ Khi dev QLHV, phải HIỂU DTLX schema vì cùng DB.**\\n\\n## Project Identity\\n- **DTLX Name**: AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) — MASTER\\n- **QLHV Name**: AHV QLHV (Quản Lý Học Viên) — SUBSYSTEM\\n- **Telegram\\n\\nSource: memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"6d33dcbcde98902d6f184f316670fd98825cd1bfa92d0d558a8ab236984c0dee\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 38,\n      \"endLine\": 60,\n      \"score\": 0.7177166514550428,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7177166514550428,\n      \"snippet\": \"### Bộ 2: Ecosystem (ahv-qlhv/*) — ĐANG DEV TRONG SESSION NÀY\\n- `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be` (id: 81078323) — Last: 2026-04-11 ✅\\n- `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe` (id: 81078350) — Last: 2026-04-11 ✅\\n- Đang hoạt động: develop + main\\n\\n### Landing Page (không đọc)\\n- `ahv-dtlx/ahv-landing-page-v2` (id: 80400174)\\n\\n## Local Workspace (QLHV — đang dev)\\n- **BE**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/`\\n- **FE**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/`\\n\\n## Database\\n- **MongoDB**: `mongodb://103.253.21.98:27017` (SHARED với DTLX)\\n- **ERD**: Confluence page `23494657` (v35) — 20+ entities\\n\\n## Agents\\n- Use prefix `ahv-dtlx:` for all spawned subagents\\n\\nSource: memory/dtlx-context.md#L38-L60\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md#L38-L60\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"518063e3e9cd5341c81c75ff2fda150670bddc7b6ab9511befb90f0125b345ff\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-14.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 29,\n      \"endLine\": 50,\n      \"score\": 0.7173014424599918,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7173014424599918,\n      \"snippet\": \"2. `/notify-users/unread/count` → 500: fallback `req.user.id` for undefined query\\n  3. `/users/sales/counter` → 500: `docCounter[0] || {}` for empty aggregate\\n  4. `/lessons/detail-by-date` → server crash: route reorder (`/:id` catchall moved after specific routes)\\n  5. `/teacher-infos` → 404: added `router.get('/')` route\\n\\n## 08:00 UTC — DTLX BE Full API Test Results (79 endpoints)\\n- **Tested:** 79 endpoints via Python script\\n- **Results:** ✅ 67 OK | ⚠️ 11 WARN | ❌ 0 ERR\\n- **WARNs (expected behavior, not bugs):** change-password (400 missing fields), refetch-token (403 expired), users/students (404 no data), users/teachers (404 no data), exam-results/me (404 no data), conventions (404 POS\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-14.md#L29-L50\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-14.md#L29-L50\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"mode\": \"fts-only\"\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"id":"07cdf349780f84851f44e5ab68761cdbe5f6e4a62559b8fbf3f07e